{"tid":792900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（呼吸plan末日）鮑威爾撐儲局循序漸進加息","createTime":"2018-08-25T02:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T03:12:14.000Z","uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64cf704b8fb1fabe3a08c5894827970ced059b37","tid":792900,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】美國聯儲局主席鮑威爾（Jerome Powell）昨晚本港時間10時於Jackson Hole全球銀行家年會演講，表明目前經濟增長勢頭、就業數據良好，通脹數據符預期，支持儲局循序漸進加息。他的演說沒有回應總統特朗普不滿聯局加息的批評。<br />\n<br />\n美股早段升　納指創新高<br />\n<br />\n受消息刺激，美股周五早段全面造好，道指升逾80點，報25740點；標普500指數再試挑戰今年1月高位2872點，升11點，報2868點；納斯達克指數曾創新高，升60點，報7939點。<br />\n港股方面，昨日延續跌勢，早市低開224點，其後受A股帶動下，午後曾倒升40點，但未能保持升勢，最終跌118點或0.43%，報27671點；H指跌35點或0.32%，報10779點；成交769億元，創本月新低。累計全周，恒指反彈458點或1.68%，H指表現較佳，升265點或2.53%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180825&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20484424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180825%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20484424&d=iiVKfFDxN4jRilkKQV7gtkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6b6de4d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180825%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20484424&h=7bdf2fcc\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180825&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20484424</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  主席撐加息 呼吸plan今次仆街了"},{"pid":"8c2e7aab4ed1efeea2730e5ad46baf11fbdf73a2","tid":792900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:42:07.000Z","msg":"一定會加啦<br />\n<br />\n否則美帝有經濟過熱風險"},{"pid":"dd62dd7f5cdc2e432e066a0317a5856f81df3c47","tid":792900,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face